of the application.\n\n3. **API Development**: Implement the API endpoints according to the defined requirements and architectural design.\n\n4. **Code Review**: Ensure the code adheres to best practices and standards.\n\n5. **Testing**: Thoroughly test the API for functionality, performance, and security.\n\nLet's start by defining the API requirements. I will outline these tasks for our specialists and gather the initial requirements.", "refusal": null, "role": "assistant", "annotations": [], "audio": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_WOl6U7wlkYIfKss2DRRFyXqQ", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\":\"data/knowledge_base\"}", "name": "board_list_directory"}, "type": "function"}]}}], "created": 1773174263, "model": "gpt-4o-2024-08-06", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "default", "system_fingerprint": "fp_c4e01d72e0", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 179, "prompt_tokens": 408, "total_tokens": 587, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 0}}}, "prompt_tokens": 408, "completion_tokens": 179, "agent_id": "ProjectManager_e5b1622b-a849-4df0-8300-e31e5a5bf270/e5b1622b-a849-4df0-8300-e31e5a5bf270"}
